summary: So I’m watching the Indigo League series of Pokemon, and I’m really enjoying it! There are some episodes that I’d watched before...
body:
So I’m watching the Indigo League series of Pokemon, and I’m really enjoying it! There are some episodes that I’d watched before but had completely forgotten about until seeing them again, and a great deal more that I’d never watched while it was running on TV, for one reason or another. Even the episodes I recalled more clearly had a lot more puns than I remembered them having, and I have to wonder if that’s where my appreciation for them came from…

I’m also watching the XY and Sun and Moon series on Netflix, too, which is pretty fun! It’ll take a while for me to catch up on all the episodes, but honestly I’m pretty happy about that, as that means it’ll take longer for me to run out of stuff to watch!
